        "text": "sqq.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Such brief anticipative summaries of a series of events afterwards described in detail are very common in Hebrew narrative.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Upon their shoulders with the staves there-on.—Literally, with their shoulder, with the poles upon themselves.",
